data.title: Today In Wrestling History Via WWE Network (08/30/2018): Lex Luger vs. Yokozuna at WWE Summerslam 1993
data.meta_description: Looking for something to watch? Delve into the WWE Network vault with Today in Wrestling History!
data.text:
As a daily feature, WWE Network News posts a comprehensive list of everything that took place on this day in wrestling history. Or at least everything that is currently available to watch on the WWE Network. This list is courtesy of the Reddit version of WWE Network Bot.

Disclaimer: Any incorrect dates are taken directly from the WWE Network’s code. Basically, they goofed, not us. If you notice any incorrect dates, feel free to leave a comment.

On PC, you can click on each link below to be taken to the corresponding show or milestone!
